Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:18.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.56,0:00:24.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,A thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:30.22,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.02,0:00:36.96,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.24,0:00:42.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:48.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:52.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,And fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:58.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\NAs the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.33,0:01:01.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:06.59,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:12.83,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,That blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:17.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:24.12,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.12,0:01:45.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All hands, level-one battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:50.26,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(81,143)}Love Drifts Away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:46.39,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:48.66,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, level-one battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to the bridge. This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:52.73,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, all hands, level-one battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:50.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.85,0:01:52.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, Milia?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.16,0:01:54.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Max.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:01:58.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going now, "Sempai."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:01:59.73,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get yourselves killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:01.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Let's go, Milia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:03.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Max!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:15.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:21.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I may never see you again,\Nso I'll just say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:25.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I...loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.03,0:02:27.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:28.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:31.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be happy with Kaifun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:45.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.26,0:02:47.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.45,0:02:49.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:50.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.99,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Work teams, switch payloads to reaction\Nwarheads on the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:03.37,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,4th Tomahawk Battery, remain on standby\Nonce the Sentinels deploy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.25,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad, move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-01, stand by for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.51,0:03:11.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reactor output climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:12.69,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Balancers normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:14.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All systems green!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:15.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.86,0:03:15.86,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:29.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the changeover to reaction\Nwarheads progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're currently at 70%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:33.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.47,0:03:37.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,About 20% of the Valkyries still\Nneed to be loaded out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:38.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have them work faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaction weaponry, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:45.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that we'd be using\Nour reaction weapons against your fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:48.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:49.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ironic indeed, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,De-fold signatures are increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:01.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get everybody into\Nthe maintenance block!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The gravity controller is at level 8.9.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Station Liberty reports that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:06.92,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy fleet is now over\Nfour million ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:10.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Cannon will reach\Ncritical in 300 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.26,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Silos 7 and 9 are now open!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A fleet of four million ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really beat them with\Nthe Grand Cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we able to communicate with\Nthe enemy fleet yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried several times, but\Nthere's still no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:24.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have no choice but to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:28.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,3rd Valkyrie interceptor units,\Nclimb to 30,000 meters and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:31.65,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,18th and 27th combat squadrons,\Ndeploy to Area A-4 at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:32.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:52.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:55.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:04:58.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I only thought of you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:11.96,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,As a friend, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:36.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships have de-folded!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:39.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. We'll strike the enemy planet first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.32,0:05:41.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, prepare for barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.88,0:05:50.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Hikaru, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I like Kaifun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:56.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault. I should have\Nmade my feelings clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:05:59.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:05.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fighter pilot and you're a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't have worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.99,0:06:09.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:18.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on a ship as small as the Macross, we're\Nliving in two totally different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Total annihilation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:57.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilated? The Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been wiped out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.40,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it done for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:18.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:24.95,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad... Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:27.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:37.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ocean filled with stardust
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.77,0:07:43.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Reflects the warm sun back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.31,0:07:48.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A little oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:55.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our home, the green Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.54,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One day we shall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:04.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over! First the Earth, and then us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I'd like to ask of you:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.79,0:08:17.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you sing? Sing for us all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:21.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:28.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damage ratio for all sections is 30%.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Grand Cannon secure?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.56,0:08:31.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be able to fire it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.86,0:08:34.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Recommence countdown at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:35.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Power generators are online.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:39.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Energy levels are climbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,T-minus 2 minutes to firing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:47.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Britai, I want your fleet to do a\Nsimultaneous translation of Lynn Minmay's song
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:50.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and transmit it on all military frequencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can do that, but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:57.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers of the Bodol Main Fleet are unaware\Nof the essence of Protoculture.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:02.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we broadcast the female's songs, they will\Nexperience a momentary culture shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:05.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing us to disrupt their\Nchain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.96,0:09:09.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And you'll use that disruption\Nto attack the Bodol flagship?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.62,0:09:12.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a foe we can beat\Nin a head-on attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.45,0:09:14.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.93,0:09:17.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Broadcasting those songs will likely boost\Nthe morale of our own men as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Global...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:23.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Miss Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.77,0:09:26.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in contact with 1st Lt. Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:29.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're working on a plan based on his idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:32.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You will sing for us, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:34.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll do whatever I can to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I have one more favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:43.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you perform a "kiss" with that\Nman who was in your movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But why a kiss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:55.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the most effective method of delivering\Na psychological shock to us Zentradi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:05.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Energy converter is online!\NPower is exceeding ignition threshold!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,T-minus 20 seconds to firing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:19.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A high-level energy signature is\Nbuilding on the enemy planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:20.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.60,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm picking up a high-level energy\Nsignature coming from the Arctic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A section of the enemy fleet\Nis being eradicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eradicated?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Displaying maximum magnification.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.57,0:10:44.78,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... That's the Grand Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.02,0:10:46.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Cannon?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Alaska Base is still there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your best, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:12.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.18,0:11:19.44,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay, stand by to start the operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.41,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:34.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, all soldiers of the Macross\Nand the Britai Adoclas Fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:39.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We will now advance through the sector\Ncleared by the Grand Cannon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:47.53,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships other than our fighters and those\Nrelaying Lynn Minmay's songs are hostiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:50.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentlemen, I expect you to\Nshow me a good fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:00.21,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:05.08,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.70,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:12.00,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Simultaneous translation is proceeding well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:18.00,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.43,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:16.08,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:24.02,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.63,0:12:31.42,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,A love sign in the big, blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:35.03,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you, you love me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:37.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these visuals?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:39.30,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's head over heels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:42.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's being broadcast over\Nour entire communications spectrum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:45.62,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,For his plane instead of me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.79,0:12:45.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We are now within firing range.\NThe enemy is not attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:47.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:49.08,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.68,0:12:47.92,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,All ships, open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:56.13,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:01.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:04.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Farewell, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:09.81,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:10.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:11.15,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,And a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:26.71,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,ATTACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:28.01,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:32.47,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Dancing in the sky, the silver wings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:35.22,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:38.35,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:41.13,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:45.66,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes of fire splitting the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.20,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.59,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:58.83,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,To save a diseased city, he has returned
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:07.58,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil's slayer! Slayer! Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.99,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shao Pai Long
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.46,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,is a very messiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:16.77,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A battleship, huh?\NOkay, I'll use reaction missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:20.86,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,The light of hope, a messiah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:24.21,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shao Pai Long!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:31.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:45.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Area A-4, please respond! Area A-4!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Area A-4!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:52.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa! You're still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:53.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lost cause here.\NGet out of here and save yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.23,0:15:03.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you were right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:10.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:17.19,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,...the fragrance of Turkish coffee fills the air
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.87,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with a listless tango rhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:26.22,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,, I'm alone and lonely, but if I dance
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:31.12,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,A breeze will blow through my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't make it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.48,0:15:35.13,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't show up
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:39.86,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who I'll be dancing with tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:42.46,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:44.68,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:49.77,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold, Shanghai dandy
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:54.75,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,The smoke from the Gitanes gets in my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.17,0:16:00.55,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"So you'll sing? You'll sing for us all?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:04.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Just for today, I'll do it only for you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.70,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Farewell, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The surface has been destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:37.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:39.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is High Command.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:42.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If anyone is still alive, please respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.02,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Captain Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.19,0:16:47.03,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice! It can't be! Is that you, Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:52.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, but it looks like I'm the\Nonly one who survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:53.14,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:57.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm coming in to get you.\NGive me your current location.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:17:00.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it will just put you in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.50,0:17:03.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I've never obeyed\Norders like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:07.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo, you... You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.35,0:17:18.47,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:23.38,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.06,0:17:33.62,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing before me, a sad look on your face
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:30.94,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.68,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:35.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:44.70,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're going off to war
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:38.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But sir! We'd be fighting our allies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:42.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I'm Kamujin the Ally Killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:55.18,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All the men, together, as if possessed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:18:01.18,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,With mouths pulled tight, with eyes burning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep up the barrage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.25,0:18:02.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Britai, don't fall behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.48,0:18:06.52,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,They march in step
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:16.96,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'll be left behind
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.62,0:18:22.80,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All for war
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:27.40,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All for pride
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:33.05,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:38.84,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.13,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:49.88,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I rot away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:50.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:05.24,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:10.46,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:21.13,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing before you, a helpless look on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:31.76,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I'll always hate war
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Approaching target!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.35,0:19:38.58,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All reaction weaponry is standing by!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:41.92,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,All the women, together, will recover
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.65,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All escort squadrons, deploy at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus the pinpoint barriers on the bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:48.06,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,With teeth clenched, with spines firm
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.72,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.49,0:19:53.50,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the children
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:09.14,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're going to return
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:19.94,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the war, all for the cause of living
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:25.64,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Time drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:30.56,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Love drifts away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:29.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Protoculture!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.34,0:20:41.30,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I rot away...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.99,0:20:58.27,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I rot away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:26.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...I guess I disobeyed\Norders again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:33.97,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:41.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I thought you\Nmight come for me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:43.88,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.87,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:54.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:56.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think everyone's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.52,0:21:57.54,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:03.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We might be the only two people\Nleft alive on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.74,0:22:06.15,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not so bad, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.25,0:22:08.90,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:10.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.38,0:22:17.78,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,A little oasis
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.38,0:22:24.78,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our home, the green Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:22.20,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.74,0:22:25.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross! They made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.18,0:22:30.02,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,One day, we shall return
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.73,0:22:27.17,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:29.21,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:36.68,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,So until then, please don't change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:37.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.22,0:22:37.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.06,0:22:48.10,songM2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Beautiful place in my heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:22:54.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:55.69,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:34.65,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(84,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:34.63,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(336,459)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:40.93,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,The hellish battle that reduced\Nthe Earth to ashes has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.46,0:23:48.34,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Those few who survived will descend\Nonto an unrecognizable world and begin working to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.55,0:23:53.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,However, new problems begin to arise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.46,0:23:58.17,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:24:01.80,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(105,143)}MY ALBUM
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:01.57,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"MY ALBUM"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.24,0:24:22.39,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:29.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.92,0:24:35.77,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.26,0:24:43.51,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.23,0:24:49.85,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.99,0:24:56.72,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.86,0:25:04.24,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.38,0:25:15.77,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
